trans-unit.source: Represents a license that enables access to protected rights managed content.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en lisens som gir tilgang til beskyttet rettigheter behandlet innhold.

trans-unit.source: As with other <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement> types, UseLicense is only usable in full trust applications.
trans-unit.target: Som med andre <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement>typer UseLicense brukes bare i fullstendig klarering programmer.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: A use license in serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] form.
trans-unit.target: En brukerlisens i serialisert [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] skjemaet.

trans-unit.source: useLicense is .
trans-unit.target: useLicenseis .

trans-unit.source: useLicense is invalid.
trans-unit.target: useLicenseer ugyldig.

trans-unit.source: Gets the application data dictionary that contains key/value pairs passed from the publishing application to the consuming application.
trans-unit.target: Henter programmet datakatalogen som inneholder nøkkel-/ verdipar som er sendt fra publisering programmet forbruk programmet.

trans-unit.source: One data key/value pair that is processed by a Rights Management Services (RMS) server is the string pair "Allow_Server_Editing"/"True".
trans-unit.target: Nøkkel/verdi-paret én data som er behandlet av en Rights Management Services (RMS)-server er paret strengen "Allow_Server_Editing" / "True".

trans-unit.source: When the issuance license "Allow_Server_Editing"/"True" is set, the service, or any trusted service, can reuse the content key.
trans-unit.target: Når utstedelse lisens "Allow_Server_Editing" / "True" er angitt, tjenesten, eller en klarert service kan bruke innholdsnøkkelen.

trans-unit.source: The key/value pair "NOLICCACHE" / "1" controls the Use License embedding policy of consuming applications.
trans-unit.target: Nøkkel/verdi-paret "NOLICCACHE" / "1" Kontrollerer brukerlisensen innebygging policyen for å bruke programmer.

trans-unit.source: When "NOLICCACHE" / "1" is set, applications are expected not to embed the Use License within the rights managed document.
trans-unit.target: Når "NOLICCACHE" / "1" er angitt, programmer forventes ikke bygge inn brukerlisensen i rights administrert dokument.

trans-unit.source: The application data dictionary that contains key/value pairs passed from the publishing application to the consuming application.
trans-unit.target: Programmet datakatalogen som inneholder nøkkel/verdi-par sendt fra publisering programmet forbruk programmet.

trans-unit.source: Binds the license to a given <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.SecureEnvironment"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Binding lisens for en gitt <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.SecureEnvironment"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: After the license is bound to a secure environment, the application can examine and exercise the rights granted by the license.
trans-unit.target: Når lisensen er bundet til en sikker miljøet, kan applikasjonen undersøke og Vær rettighetene i lisensavtalen.

trans-unit.source: The returned <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider> instance provides decryption and access to the protected rights managed content.
trans-unit.target: Det returnerte <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider>forekomsten gir dekryptering og tilgang til beskyttet rettigheter behandlet innhold.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider>

trans-unit.source: The environment to bind the license to.
trans-unit.target: Miljøet ikke binde lisensen til.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider"></xref> instance if the license binding succeeded; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Security.RightsManagement.CryptoProvider"> </xref> serverforekomsten hvis lisensen bindingen lyktes; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: secureEnvironment is .
trans-unit.target: secureEnvironmentis .

trans-unit.source: Gets the content identifier created by the publisher.
trans-unit.target: Henter innhold-ID som er opprettet av utgiveren.

trans-unit.source: ContentId is created by the publisher and can be used to match content to a <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense> and <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>.
trans-unit.target: Innholds-ID er opprettet av utgiveren, og kan brukes til å samsvare med innholdet til en <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>og <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense>.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.PublishLicense> </xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense>

trans-unit.source: The content identifier created by the publisher.
trans-unit.target: Innhold-ID er opprettet av utgiveren.

trans-unit.source: Indicates if this license is equivalent to another given license.
trans-unit.target: Angir om denne lisensen er tilsvarende til en annen gitt lisens.

trans-unit.source: Equals tests for equivalence comparing the serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] strings specified to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A> constructors.
trans-unit.target: Er lik tester likhet sammenligne den serialiserte [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] strenger som er angitt til den <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>konstruktører.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The license to compare.
trans-unit.target: Lisens til å sammenligne.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if both licenses are the equivalent; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis begge lisenser tilsvarer; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code associated with this license.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer hash-kode assosiert med denne lisensen.

trans-unit.source: The returned hash code is based on the serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] string passed to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Returnerte hash-koden er basert på den serialiserte [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] streng som er sendt til den <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: A hash code for this license.
trans-unit.target: En hash-kode for denne lisensen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the owner of the license.
trans-unit.target: Henter eieren av lisensen.

trans-unit.source: The license owner is obtained from the serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] string passed to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Lisenseieren hentes fra den serialiserte [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] streng som er sendt til den <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>konstruktør.</xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The owner of the license.
trans-unit.target: Eieren av lisensen.

trans-unit.source: Returns the serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xrml-md.md)] string used to create this license.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer den serialiserte [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xrml-md.md)] Formatstrengen som brukes til å opprette denne lisensen.

trans-unit.source: The serialized [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] string originally passed to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Den serialiserte [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xrml](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] streng opprinnelig ble sendt til den <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UseLicense.%23ctor%2A> konstruktør.
